nhc_headline: ...AIR FORCE RESERVE HURRICANE HUNTERS INVESTIGATING JERRY...
summary: ...AIR FORCE RESERVE HURRICANE HUNTERS INVESTIGATING JERRY... As of 2:00 PM AST Wed Oct 08 the center of Jerry was located near 14.3, -53.7 with movement WNW at 23 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
